---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Section from "../components/ui/Section.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Contato — Comitê Anti-Imperialista Abreu e Lima">
  <main>
    <Section title="Contato" subtitle="Fale com o Comitê (placeholder).">
      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
        <form class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 p-6">
          <label class="block text-sm font-medium">Nome</label>
          <input class="mt-2 w-full rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 px-3 py-2" placeholder="Lorem Ipsum" />

          <label class="mt-4 block text-sm font-medium">E-mail</label>
          <input class="mt-2 w-full rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 px-3 py-2" placeholder="lorem@ipsum.org" />

          <label class="mt-4 block text-sm font-medium">Mensagem</label>
          <textarea class="mt-2 min-h-[120px] w-full rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 px-3 py-2" placeholder="Lorem ipsum..." />

          <button type="button" class="mt-4 rounded-full border border-neutral-900 px-5 py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-neutral-900 hover:text-white">
            Enviar (MVP)
          </button>

          <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-neutral-500">
            No MVP, o formulário pode virar um mailto:, webhook ou serviço simples. (Sem backend aqui ainda.)
          </p>
        </form>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 p-6">
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold">Canais</div>
          <div class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-neutral-700">
            <div><span class="text-neutral-500">E-mail:</span> contato@exemplo.org</div>
            <div><span class="text-neutral-500">Redes:</span> @exemplo</div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-6 rounded-xl bg-neutral-50 p-4 text-xs text-neutral-600">
            Dica: quando vocês definirem o domínio, a gente ajusta tudo para SEO e indexação com HTTPS + DNSLink.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Section>
  </main>

</BaseLayout>
